&lt;h6&gt;加權股價指數近 6 個月價量表現：&lt;/h6&gt;

&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;（資料來源：Bloomberg, 截至2023/3/15）&quot; data-height=&quot;161&quot; data-mime=&quot;image/jpeg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;4.490683229813665&quot; data-src-m=&quot;https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5115761/m/752e45ba2f3924faa3498cfc6509ab61.jpg&quot; data-width=&quot;723&quot; src=&quot;https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5115761/l/752e45ba2f3924faa3498cfc6509ab61.jpg&quot;&gt;
